data.description: Immaculately maintained two-bedroom townhome in the gated community of Village of Sewickley Hills. Great room open floor plan concept with 9-foot ceilings, granite kitchen with white cabinetry. Bosch Dishwaser and newer stainless-steel refrigerator. Cozy corner gas fireplace in living room. Upstairs features two bedrooms, each with an en-suite bath and walk in closet. First floor laundry and half bath. New hot water tank recently installed. This is a gated community with a clubhouse party room, a pool, a movie room, personal office and fitness center. Convenient location with easy access to both I-79 and I-279 and surrounding amenities.
